high_descs: Go straight to the wall, turn right, go straight, turn right at the start of the counter on the right.
Take the knife next to the salt on the counter.
Turn left, go straight to the counter, turn right, go straight then turn left at the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into pieces.
Turn left, go straight to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around, go back to the sink on the left.
Take a piece of apple from the sink.
Turn right, go straight, turn right, go straight then turn left at the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge on the upper shelf to the left of the tomato. Close then open the fridge. Take the apple from the fridge.
Turn left, go straight, at the counter turn let, go straight to the microwave.
Put the apple piece in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of apple in a microwave.

high_descs: Move forward, then right, then face the brown table to your right.
Take the knife on the brown table in front of you.
Turn left, then right, then face the sink on your left.
Slice the apple in the sink in front of you.
Turn left and face the microwave in front of you.
Open the microwave in front of you, place the knife inside and close the microwave.
Turn around and face the sink on your left.
Take an apple slice from the sink in front of you.
Turn right, then right again around the counter and face the fridge to your left.
Open the fridge, place the apple slice inside, close it, take out the apple slice, then close the fridge.
Turn left, then left again and face the microwave on the counter in front of you.
Open the microwave, place the apple slice inside and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold apple slice in the microwave.

high_descs: walk straight ahead, then turn right and walk over to the beginning part of the kitchen island on your right
take a butter knife off of that kitchen island counter top
turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink at the end of the room but kind of a bit to the right
cut up the green apple inside of the kitchen sink
turn left and walk over to the microwave at the end of the room
place the butter knife down inside of the microwave
turn around and walk back over to the kitchen sink on the left
grab an apple slice out of the sink
turn right and walk over to the fridge that is somewhat to the right, it is at the end of the room though
place the apple slice inside of the fridge, close the door of course, then let it cool for while.  Once it is done cooling open the door and take it back out, then close the door
turn left and walk to the kitchen counters at the end of the room, then do a sharp left turn to end up walk to the end of the room where the microwave is
place the apple slice right there in the microwave, open the door first though, and then close it when you're done
anns.task_desc: place an cooled apple slice inside of the microwave

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the kitchen island, stop at the end with the chair and the utensils.
Pick up the knife that is in front of the salt shaker.
Turn and walk toward the sink.
Slice the apple that is near the back of the sink.
Turn to your left and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave door and place the knife at the inside back of the microwave, close the microwave door, turn it on.
Turn towards your right and go back to the sink.
Pick up the wedge of the apple nearest the faucet.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.

Open the fridge door and place the apple wedge on the shelf with the tomato, to the left of the tomato, close the fridge door; after cooling open the fridge door, pick up the apple wedge, close the fridge door.
Turn to your left and walk to the microwave oven.
Open the microwave door and put the apple wedge at the front of the plate in the microwave, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple, refrigerate it, and microwave it

high_descs: Turn to the right, go to the counter in the center of the room.
Pick up the butter knife next to the salt.
Turn to the left, walk to the sink.
Cut the green apple in the sink.
Turn to the left, walk to the microwave.
Put the butter knife in the back of the microwave.
Turn around, go back to the sink.
Pick up a piece of the cut apple.
Turn to the right, walk to the counter, turn to the left, walk to the refrigerator.
Put the apple piece next to the tomato in the refrigerator for a few seconds, get the piece of apple.
Turn to the left, walk to the counter, turn to the left, walk  to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the cold apple in the microwave.
